title: Ardell Brow Perfection Stencils 4 Stencils
description: Buy Ardell Eye Brow Makeup - Ardell Brow Perfection Stencils 4 Stencils. How-to-Use: Use both hands to line stencil up with the natural shape of your brow, paying particular attention to the inner edge of brow and highest point of arch. Using one hand, hold stencil in place with our thumb and index finger. Using a brow pencil in the other hand, use light strokes in the same direction as hair growth to fill in brows. For other brow, turn stencil over and repeat steps.
